data.description: Come view this lovely dream home in southern Harris County in the sought after Callaway Woods subdivision. This stunning home has 4 bedrooms with the master on main and a half bath on the main floor. The large kitchen with an island has a nice open view into the large living room as well as a breakfast area. The home sits on over 2 acres with a large backyard which includes a large 50x20 RV garage with plenty of storage! There is a lovely saltwater pool that has electric awnings as well as an enclosed sunroom with a jacuzzi. The home has plantation shutters throughout as well as a gas log fireplace. The upstairs has 3 bedrooms with 2 full baths as well as a large attic space that has plenty of storage space or you could convert it into a game room/office or an extra bedroom. Give me a call today to schedule a showing to view this lovely home!
